{"tid":2494834,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla無人駕駛｜Model S德州高速入迴旋處失控撞樹 焚燒四小時兩死「司機位無人」","createTime":"2021-04-18T22:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T22:50:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"227fe5c56e94ecbbfb79b4e50e5f71243b9e3b20","tid":2494834,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:27:25.000Z","msg":"哈里斯縣警員赫爾曼（Mark Herman）表示，肇事2019年Model S高速進入迴旋處時失控，事發時無人在司機位，一人在前座乘客位，一人在後座。<br />\n<br />\n車主的內兄弟說，車主說駕車與一位好友兜風，因此事發時車上只有兩人。他懷疑車主開車後啟動Autopilot自動輔助駕駛系統，然後移到後座，惟車行了幾百米後出事。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210419/5OIJ5YYJRBHZFBFB5QUEU3JBDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210419%2F5OIJ5YYJRBHZFBFB5QUEU3JBDI%2F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=f4a3ff15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210419%2F5OIJ5YYJRBHZFBFB5QUEU3JBDI%2F&h=8472e588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210419/5OIJ5YYJRBHZFBFB5QUEU3JBDI/</a>"},{"pid":"d9392bbd7a165e35212ea89c9b9eec046462cfab","tid":2494834,"uid":132713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:29:54.000Z","msg":"On99<br />\n揸住車唔傾得計咩<br />\n而家累死埋個fd"},{"pid":"27c6f0e31b7213a295a7a039d204927c3140df3e","tid":2494834,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:35:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">車主開車後啟動Autopilot自動輔助駕駛系統，然後移到後座，惟車行了幾百米後出事。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\non9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你事先唔知唔可以隻手離開車盤<br />\n你啟動左後個mon都會提醒你多次<br />\n智商堪憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695426ac091f1d8d5607580dc24169cca777eb38","tid":2494834,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27c6f0e31b7213a295a7a039d204927c3140df3e","tid":2494834,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislik